            <lg xml:id="TK637">
<l>ceyaṟkai yaṟintak kaṭaittu mulakat </l>
<l>tiyaṟkai yaṟintu ceyal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Though you are acquainted with the (theoretical) methods (of performing an act), understand the ways of the world and act accordingly.</l>
